languages.text: "Благодарю, Ваша Светлость, все целы. Молодчик бесноватый, но, по сравнению с пожаром в топливном отсеке, выглядел угрозой на троечку".
"Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, not a scratch on us. He's a piece of work, right enough, but he's no fuel compartment fire. More like a sparking cogitator."
languages.original_text: "Благодарю, Ваша Светлость, все целы. Молодчик бесноватый, но, по сравнению с пожаром в топливном отсеке, выглядел угрозой на троечку".

traits.locale_text: "Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, we're all in one piece. The lad is feisty, but he's no compression cascade. We've faced worse hazards."

languages.text: «Gracias, mi{mf|lord|lady}. Estamos todos ilesos. Nos dio guerra, pero hemos apagado peores incendios. Mucho ruido y pocas nueces».
languages.original_text: "Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, not a scratch on us. He's a piece of work, right enough, but he's no fuel compartment fire. More like a sparking cogitator."

traits.locale_text: «Gracias, mi{mf|lord|lady}. Estamos todos ilesos. Nos dio guerra, pero hemos apagado peores incendios. Mucho ruido y pocas nueces».

languages.text: 「ありがとうございます、陛下。全員無事です。彼は確かに素晴らしい仕事ぶりですが、火種にはなりません。火花を散らすコジテーターのようなものです」
languages.original_text: "Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, not a scratch on us. He's a piece of work, right enough, but he's no fuel compartment fire. More like a sparking cogitator."

traits.locale_text: 「ありがとうございます、陛下。全員無事です。彼は確かに素晴らしい仕事ぶりですが、火種にはなりません。火花を散らすコジテーターのようなものです」

languages.text: “谢谢您，大人，我们一点事都没有。说真的，虽然这家伙挺不好对付，但他和四处着火的船舱根本没法比，他最多就算是个冒着火星的沉思者。”
languages.original_text: "Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, not a scratch on us. He's a piece of work, right enough, but he's no fuel compartment fire. More like a sparking cogitator."

traits.locale_text: “谢谢您，大人，我们一点事都没有。说真的，虽然这家伙挺不好对付，但他和四处着火的船舱根本没法比，他最多就算是个冒着火星的沉思者。”

languages.text: "Danke, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}. Wir haben nicht einen Kratzer." Er ist eine harte Nuss, das schon, aber er ist kein Feuer im Treibstoffmodul. Eher ein Funken sprühender Cogitator."
languages.original_text: "Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, not a scratch on us. He's a piece of work, right enough, but he's no fuel compartment fire. More like a sparking cogitator."

traits.locale_text: "Danke, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}. Wir haben nicht einen Kratzer." Er ist eine harte Nuss, das schon, aber er ist kein Feuer im Treibstoffmodul. Eher ein Funken sprühender Cogitator."

languages.text: « Tout va bien, Votre Seigneurie, merci de votre sollicitude. Il n'est certes pas très coopératif, mais ses gesticulations évoquent davantage un cogitateur défectueux qu'un incendie dans le réservoir de carburant. »
languages.original_text: "Thank you, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, not a scratch on us. He's a piece of work, right enough, but he's no fuel compartment fire. More like a sparking cogitator."

languages.text: "Teşekkürlerimi sunuyorum {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Burnumuz dahi kanamadı. Aşağılığın teki olduğuna kuşku yok ama kompartıman yangınını körükleyecek kadar değil. Bundan en fazla kavramsayardan çıkan bir kıvılcım olur."
